Best Regards

Shahrukh Ijaz

reviews.comment: this seller built a website called actorshut.com - the website first of all took forever to build. next the seller kept trying to charge me more money. then when the website was finally done. I decided to test the website. when I got the test back. the website has a ton of problems that the developer never fixed. now the seller is ignoring my messages. I have already contacted Fiverr to get my money back and have his account closed. buyer beware. this seller is the worst on fiverr. RUN...

seller_response.comment: The website is same as your reference, put extra work into this website but you're not satisfied after offering too much work for free. Last thing I have asked for extra money for your 56 new changes which were not there in scope of project as well.

reviews.comment: He was very patient with me. I needed to change my billing and add pages and it took me longer than I thought it would but he kept working with me until we got everything worked out.
This was a difficult project because I had to add pages and couldn't get SquareSpace to help me change my account. But he was patient as we worked through the problems.
Second order. Very happy. Will work with him again.

Shahrukh is very skillful and professional.  He designed and built me a website from scratch.  He also delivered it online.  

I am very inexperienced in this arena and he held my hand all the way through. 

I am sure I was annoying, sorry Shahrukh .

seller_response.comment: haha, No all good so far really enjoy work with you!

reviews_snippet.comment:
I am thrilled to share my experience working with Shahrukh, who has been our go-to Python web scraping specialist for the past year. His expertise in Python and web scraping technologies has consistently exceeded our expectations. Shahrukh demonstrates an exceptional grasp of various scraping libraries, including BeautifulSoup, Scrapy, and Selenium, and applies them with remarkable efficiency.

Over the past year, Shahrukh has handled a wide range of complex projects, from extracting data from dynamic websites to handling CAPTCHAs and proxy rotation. His solutions are not only effective but also scalable.

Delivered an exceptional product on time and leverage his knowledge to contribute to the quality of the final product.
Very easy to work with.
I have an appreciation for his being ranked a PRO.  He applied himself to the project and delivered on time.  Great guy
replying very fast , making good and nice work , was happy to work with you and hopefully we will again.

The seller was swift to respond and was very helpful in making all the necessary changes. I am pleased with the outcome and highly recommend their services.
Thanks, Lin - UK
